name: Rosetta Pillow in Liberty
description:
The Liberty colorway evokes childhood memories of the Fourth of July. Based on a dress made by my mother, I remember watching her sew the amazing clothes she made for me as a child. 

Each print is designed by me and then digitally printed onto linen-cotton canvas. Once I have ensured color accuracy, I decide on trim or embellishment and sew them into these one of a kind pillows just for you! Each handmade double stitched pillow is made of high quality linen cotton and filled with a hypo-allergenic poly fill.

Please note that each pillow will differ from the images depending on where I cut in the fabric. Rest assured that I will determine each cut to give you the best pillow possible. Measures 18"x18".

I can also do customized colors on any of the prints to match your personal preferences.

International shipping is available just contact me for quotes.
